<s> Yes, this makes no sense at all.  </s>
<s> This should say something along the lines of: Synthesized speech is critical for individuals who are blind and for many people with the reading difficulties that often accompany cognitive disabilities, and learning disabilities.  </s>
<s> Non-text equivalents are helpful for individuals who have reading difficulties associated with deafness.  </s>
